! Extending the Editor

!! Custom Editor Actions

Add toolbar and slash-menu items by creating tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/ProseMirror/EditorAction` with:

|!Field |!Description |
|`action-id` |Built-in command id (e.g. `bold`, `heading1`, `insert-table`) |
|`caption` |Display label |
|`description` |Tooltip / slash-menu description |
|`category` |`inline-format`, `block-type`, `block-insert`, or `other` |
|`icon` |Tiddler title of an SVG icon |
|`keyboard-shortcut` |PM keymap string (e.g. `Mod-b`) or `none` |

!! Custom Snippets

Any tiddler tagged `$:/tags/TextEditor/Snippet` appears in the slash menu. If the snippet text is a pragma (e.g. `\procedure`), it is inserted as a visual pragma block.

!! Architecture

The editor is built on [[ProseMirror|https://prosemirror.net/]]:

* ''Schema'' (`schema.js`): defines PM node/mark types corresponding to WikiText constructs
* ''AST conversion'' (`ast/`): bidirectional conversion between TW parse tree and PM document JSON
* ''Engine'' (`engine.js`): implements the TW editor engine interface
* ''Widget'' (`widget.js`): the `$prosemirror` and `edit-prosemirror` widgets
* ''Plugins'' (`editor-plugins/`): bubble menu, drag handle, link tooltip, markdown shortcuts, block placeholder
